  <h3>3000 BCE</h3>
  <p>Writing developed in ancient civilizations</p>
  
  <div class="hidden">
    <p>Earliest writing emerged in Sumer, Egypt, and the Indus Valley to record information and transactions.</p>
    
    <img src="writing.jpg">
    
    <blockquote>"The invention of writing revolutionized human culture and knowledge transfer."</blockquote>
  </div>
