<div class="entry">  
  <h3>600 BCE</h3>
  <p>Pythagoras' mathematical theorems in ancient Greece</p>

  <div class="hidden">
    <p>Pythagoras established foundational mathematical contributions like the Pythagorean theorem.</p>
    
    <img src="pythagoras.jpg">
    
    <blockquote>"Do not say a little in many words but a great deal in a few." - Pythagoras</blockquote>
  </div>
</div>

